OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779120674
OL,3,CNorth of England bid to host 2040s
OL,4,COlympics and Paralympics assessment to
OL,5,Cbegin
OL,7,FA bid to stage the Olympic and
OL,8,FParalympic Games in the north of
OL,9,FEngland in the 2040s is to enter the
OL,10,Finitial assessment phase, the
OL,11,Fgovernment has announced.
OL,13,FThe government has commissioned UK
OL,14,FSport to conduct the assessment, which
OL,15,Fwill look into potential cost,
OL,16,Fregeneration of towns and cities in
OL,17,Fthe north of England and the bid's
OL,18,Fchance of success.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
