PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779120674
OL,3,CNorth of England bid to host 2040s
OL,4,COlympics and Paralympics assessment to
OL,5,Cbegin
OL,7,FIf it did succeed, it would be the
OL,8,Ffirst Games staged in Britain since
OL,9,FLondon 2012.
OL,11,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy said:
OL,12,F"London 2012 showed what the Olympics
OL,13,Fcan do for our country. It inspired a
OL,14,Fgeneration through sport, attracted
OL,15,Fhuge investment and showed the best of
OL,16,FBritain to the world.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779120674
OL,3,CNorth of England bid to host 2040s
OL,4,COlympics and Paralympics assessment to
OL,5,Cbegin
OL,7,F"But while the north of England has
OL,8,Fdriven so much sporting excellence, no
OL,9,Fmatter the talent we produce, the
OL,10,Fsporting moments we create and the
OL,11,Fworld-class events we attract ` for
OL,12,Ftoo long we have been told the
OL,13,FOlympics is simply too big and too
OL,14,Fimportant to be hosted in the north.
OL,16,F"Not any more. It's time the Olympics
OL,17,Fcame north and we showed what we can
OL,18,Foffer to the world.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779120674
OL,3,CNorth of England bid to host 2040s
OL,4,COlympics and Paralympics assessment to
OL,5,Cbegin
OL,7,F"I couldn't be more pleased to
OL,8,Fannounce that we're starting the
OL,9,Ffiring gun on a long overdue vote of
OL,10,Fconfidence in the north."
OL,12,FPart of the assessment will also look
OL,13,Fat stadium regeneration plans,
OL,14,Fincluding the government working with
OL,15,Fsports clubs and leagues to deliver
OL,16,Fimprovements to existing stadiums and
OL,17,Ftheir surrounding areas.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
