PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779120674
OL,3,CNorth of England bid to host 2040s
OL,4,COlympics and Paralympics assessment to
OL,5,Cbegin
OL,7,FPlanned projects across England at
OL,8,Fthis stage include proposals for
OL,9,FNewcastle, Greater Manchester,
OL,10,FBirmingham, Leeds, Liverpool and
OL,11,FLondon.
OL,13,FNorth East Mayor and chair of The
OL,14,FGreat North Kim McGuinness said: "From
OL,15,Four great cities and towns to our
OL,16,Fcoastlines and countryside, the north
OL,17,Fhas the venues, the passion and the
OL,18,Fsporting pride to deliver a world-
OL,19,Fclass Olympic and Paralympic Games
OL,20,Fthat showcases the very best of Great
OL,21,FBritain to the world.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779120674
OL,3,CNorth of England bid to host 2040s
OL,4,COlympics and Paralympics assessment to
OL,5,Cbegin
OL,7,F"A Great North Olympics would be a
OL,8,Fglobal showcase, leaving a legacy of
OL,9,Fprosperity, unity and renewal. It's an
OL,10,Fopportunity not to be missed,
OL,11,Fdelivering transformational investment
OL,12,Fin transport, regeneration and public
OL,13,Fspaces across the north of England.
OL,15,F"This could become the most people-
OL,16,Fpowered Games ever hosted: inspiring
OL,17,Fmillions of people into sport,
OL,18,Fvolunteering and community action."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
