PN,42407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779120674
OL,3,CNorth of England bid to host 2040s
OL,4,COlympics and Paralympics assessment to
OL,5,Cbegin
OL,7,FThe announcement has come after
OL,8,Fnorthern mayors wrote to the
OL,9,Fgovernment in February calling for it
OL,10,Fto back a bid to host the Games in the
OL,11,Fnorth of England.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
